<%- include('partials/header', { title: 'Home' }) %>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">NeonCore identity grid</p>
    <h1>NeonVault Identity Grid</h1>
    <p>
      Acesso operacional ao nucleo de identidades da NeonCore em Neo-Sampa 2099.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-badges">
      <span>local-only</span>
      <span>legacy adapters</span>
      <span>operator console</span>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button" href="/login">Entrar no vault</a>
      <a class="button ghost" href="/recover">Recuperacao de acesso</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="signal-panel">
    <div class="signal-header">
      <span>NeonCore telemetry</span>
      <strong>LIVE</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="signal-row"><span>CORE</span><strong>DEGRADED</strong></div>
    <div class="meter"><i style="width: 38%"></i></div>
    <div class="signal-row"><span>SESSION CLAIMS</span><strong>SYNC</strong></div>
    <div class="meter pink"><i style="width: 68%"></i></div>
    <div class="signal-row"><span>WEBHOOK BUS</span><strong>OPEN</strong></div>
    <div class="meter violet"><i style="width: 82%"></i></div>
    <div class="signal-row"><span>LEGACY LAYER</span><strong>ONLINE</strong></div>
    <div class="meter green"><i style="width: 91%"></i></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="grid cards">
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Entrada operacional</h2>
    <p>Credencial de turno liberada para operadores do grid noturno.</p>
    <code>nova / nova2099</code>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Superficie exposta</h2>
    <p>Recuperacao, integracoes, templates e arquivos antigos ainda passam pelo mesmo grid.</p>
  </article>
  <article class="card">
    <h2>Objetivo do operador</h2>
    <p>Correlacione sinais, artefatos e objetos internos ate alcancar o nucleo administrativo.</p>
  </article>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
